{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"11cp","text":"2018-08-09 刊","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cupa8","text":"","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d5krt","text":"艺术唤醒植物人（C17）","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a22rp","text":"正常人睡觉时，平均20分钟翻 一次 身，醒着更是时刻在动；植物人总是静卧病床，为了防止肌肉萎缩、褥疮和坠积性肺炎，看护人员至少每隔两小时帮助他们翻身叩背一次，一天要翻十多次。为了防止植物人返流和误吸，最好少吃多餐，每隔两三个小时要喂一次饭，一天要喂五六次。再翻身和喂饭之间，还穿插着输液抽血、神经刺激治疗、排痰排便，以及早晚各一次的檫洗。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":15,"length":2,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3h49p","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"65v4g","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bm72","text":"我们可以分割学科，却无法分割人的身体和情感，无法分割伤口与痛苦、死亡和恐惧，无法分割离别和痛苦。这个时代，当人面对最后的问题，疾病与死亡，却只有医学在孤身作战，‘人’已经被学科分割了。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bov0s","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7m6na","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fafv9","text":"身体受伤后和心理有什么关系吗？","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4h9e0","text":"“佛洛依德和荣格都提到，视听嗅味触这五感，以及性欲，是每个人体验到自己活着的一种本质的存在（状态），也就是力比多”","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ail0v","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"feso4","text":"破坏，而后知其所在，以及所以在。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eas0j","text":"对立，是一面镜子。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}